                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p><a href="#{nameTokens.getRegister}">Getting to
                            <br/>
                            Quebec City</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p><a href="#{nameTokens.getRegister}">Convention
